'''Billy Mays''' used to be [[an hero|an American Hero]] famous for his [[television|TV]] sales pitches that sold generations of [[fat|outstanding]] citizens a wide range of ass-kicking products and [[Hookers and blow| for knowing how to live life to the fullest]]. You probably knew Billy Mays as that guy in the [[blue]] shirt that was always screaming at you about the [[awesome]]ness of his products from behind your television screen during infomercials, thus intimidating you into [[Prank call|calling in]] and purchasing something you didn't actually need. It is this unnerving high pitched squealing that has earned him Consumerama's "Naked Mole Rats of Marketing Award" in the lulzy field of [http://www.consumerama.net/nmr/winners.html "Shameless Consumer Abuse"]. Shortly before his death, he starred in a [[TV]] show called [[Gentlemen|''Pitchmen'']], about his career. Before Mays's death he was building a new house, a house that would be his own personal Xanadu, which included a five car garage filled with his favorite white powder (And no, I don't mean Oxyclean!) The house is now owned and operated by his widow, and is located on Lake Robinson in Greer: Greenville, SC, 29550


__TOC__

In addition to his [[work]] in marketing some of the baddest household cleaning/maintenance shit the world has ever seen, Mays was also an early pioneer and expert in the field of [[EXTREME ADVERTISING]], due to his aggressive marketing style and unexplainable need to always speak in [[ALL CAPS]]. He was additionally somewhat [[notable]] for [http://au.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20080527182939AAGD0UH looking like] a [[bear]] but was "[[not gay]]" [[Wikipedia:Billy_mays#Personal_life|according to TOW]].

{{quote|His signature yelling approach to pitching an array of products, along with his recognizable '''[[Wise Beard Man|beard]]''', have gained Mays a substantial amount of recognition.|And that's from fucking [[Wikipedia]] so you [[lie|know it's true]]. - [[Wikipedia:Billy_Mays|TOW]]}}

Billy Mays died just days after [[Michael Jackson]], also from a heart attack, at the same age of 50. This was most likely [[Death Note|Kira's]] doing, because he is a fucking egotistical bastard.

